Package: PMlsspca
Type: Package
Title: Least Squares Sparse Principal Components Analysis
Version: 1.0.1
Date: 2026-02-12
Author: Giovanni M. Merola
Maintainer: <merolagio@gmail.com>
Description: Implements least-squares sparse PCA using sequential residualization and subset selection. The approach follows Merola G. M. ``2015 Sparse Principal Component Analysis: a Least Squares Approach. Australian & New Zealand J. of Statistics. 57(3)'' and  Merola G. M, Chen G. 2019 ``Projection sparse principal component analysis: An efficient least squares method''. Journal of Multivariate Analysis. 173. pp. 366-382.
License: What license is it under?
Encoding: UTF-8
